    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>VAR Hoisting </h1>
    <p>We can Initialize variable before or after it is decleared!</p>
    <b><script>
        x="Hello";
        var x;
        document.write(x);
    </script></b>


    <h1>LET Hoisting</h1>
    <p>We cannot Initialize variable before it is decleared!</p>
    <script>
        z = "Hello";
        let z;
        document.write(z);
    </script>


    <h1>LET Hoisting</h1>
    <p>We can Initialize variable after it is decleared! as like as in C</p>
    <b><script>
        let y;
        y = "Hello";
        document.write(y);
    </script></b>

    
</body>
</html>